#######################################################################################
#######################  README FOR FINAL PROJECT  ####################################
#######################################################################################

Three Servers have been installed and configured on AWS
	
	1) Web Server and Mail Server
	2) Database Server
	3) Nagios Server

Each server has been installed with Nagios Agent for Monitoring.

The SERVER DOCUMENTATION and CONFIG files for each of the three Servers have been uploaded 
on GITHUB and kept in three separate folders as below: 
	
	1) MailServer_Apache
	2) MySql_Server
	3) NagiosServer


